{
  "3020550": {
    "name": "夺宝砖家",
    "steam_appid": 3020550,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/dd6e349d27aa6a354ee9c533c3f1ff59.avif?t=1768383015\" width=513 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/ba29baf9580db7f9752522ecc7f234d5.poster.avif?t=1768383015\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/ba29baf9580db7f9752522ecc7f234d5.webm?t=1768383015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/ba29baf9580db7f9752522ecc7f234d5.mp4?t=1768383015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一款以操作和策略决定胜负的轻度肉鸽×三消解谜类游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙融合了肉鸽的随机性、三消的爽快感与解谜的策略性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由搭配强化道具，在限定步数内达成目标分数吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/9802949385cd5b4468d51100a725cd1b.avif?t=1768383015\" width=519 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/5053d68d3bec51be4bee0b4f4433765e.poster.avif?t=1768383015\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/5053d68d3bec51be4bee0b4f4433765e.webm?t=1768383015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/5053d68d3bec51be4bee0b4f4433765e.mp4?t=1768383015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了传统三消一成不变的模式？《夺宝砖家》独创的「魔方滑动」玩法将带来截然不同的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >横向或是纵向？自由移动选中的方块到任意位置，触发超乎想象的连锁反应！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/1eb103582f17da0726b882299852d5d6.avif?t=1768383015\" width=515 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/92f7bb19381a4b9d579388827bfedd59.avif?t=1768383015\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局通关后，都能选择各具特色的「遗物」，合理搭配不同遗物，让其释放最大的增益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「达成4消除即可生成特殊方块」，「同时消除3种或以上颜色，积分倍率提升」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「持有的金币越多，获得的分数越高」更多遗物等你来解锁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/f8796bc242041540c30344d6b1f8fcbf.avif?t=1768383015\" width=514 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/64e7b74379c0b1628bbc709930f80104.poster.avif?t=1768383015\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/64e7b74379c0b1628bbc709930f80104.webm?t=1768383015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受《夺宝砖家》独特的八人大逃杀模式，在限定的时间内达成最多的消除，数轮对决后，积分最高的人将会胜出！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >干扰对手还是强化自身？选择合适的遗物，你的谋略决定了你能走多远。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果想赢，绝不能手下留情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/03bea66c218c0604be9497890f61afeb.avif?t=1768383015\" width=516 height=83 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/4437ab2c3ca81ee381393a6f927e0b77.poster.avif?t=1768383015\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/4437ab2c3ca81ee381393a6f927e0b77.webm?t=1768383015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各具特色的「像素角色」将与你一同夺宝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果不慎闯关失败，可爱的像素角色将会以意想不到的方式「被处刑」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而闯关成功时BOSS也会被「华丽处决」。快来滑动这块神秘的石板，解开远古遗迹的秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>—作为寻宝猎人，为了追寻能实现心愿的秘宝，在棋盘风格的世界中踏上了冒险之旅—</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020550/extras/754072575ed053d4bd9fcd1b0485489c.avif?t=1768383015\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标，是挑战守护着秘宝的「沙漠斯芬克斯」「灼热遗迹之龙」「海底神殿克拉肯」等强大首领，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将他们一一讨伐，解开远古谜题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而不只是世界各地的冒险家，就连盗贼们也纷纷加入其中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们又各自怀揣着怎样的心愿和目的……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既然如此，那不妨投身这场秘宝之争，最终实现自己的心愿吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>更多角色、BOSS和其他内容将在正式版上线，敬请期待！</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: right\">【其乐id:1850913】</p>",
